overview: Fell running is more than a sport - it is part of an identity. Through the evocation of a poem, ‘I Am a Fellrunner’ explores the way in which one woman is defined as a fellrunner in the place where she belongs.  A film by Jessie Leong and Julie Carter.
tagline: Fell running is more than a sport - it is part of an identity.
title: I Am a Fellrunner
